  "name": "Automatic Writing",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/spells/light-royal-1.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once per day, you can spend a full hour in uninterrupted meditation. During this period, your hands produce mysterious writing that pertains to the future. At 1st level, the prophetic writing manifests as an @Compendium[pf1.spells.d1wxnax51cecplm4]{Augury} spell with 90% effectiveness.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, the writing takes the form of a @Compendium[pf1.spells.pwueht12qqo0268e]{Divination} with 90% effectiveness.</p>\n<p>At 8th level, the writing manifests as a casting of @Compendium[pf1.spells.p2kosvizylhy8vfa]{Commune} with no material component required.</p>"
    },
